{{zh-hanzi|[[一]][[蹴]][[而]][[就]]}}
==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: yī cù ér jiù

===Idiom===
# to reach the goal in one step; happen all at once
#: ''[[人民币]][[汇率]][[改革]][[不会]]'''一蹴而就'''.'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#: ''[[人民幣]][[匯率]][[改革]][[不會]]'''一蹴而就'''.'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#: ''It is unlikely that the [[renminbi|RMB]] exchange rate reforms will '''happen all at once'''.

===Related terms===
*[[一蹴可幾]], [[一蹴可几]]

